109
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:20,362
<i>”Hollowface wanted
the boy's face"</i>

110
00:13:20,440 --> 00:13:22,249
<i>“more than anything
else in the world."</i>

111
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:24,486
<i>"Without a face,"</i>

112
00:13:26,040 --> 00:13:27,166
