from his parents."

116
00:13:35,520 --> 00:13:37,124
"Then he'd take him
back to his lair."

117
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:40,167
"He'd rip off his face
and wear it himself."

118
00:13:41,120 --> 00:13:43,851
"That way,
everybody would love him."

119
00:13:45,720 --> 00:13:46,721
"The next night,."

120
00:13:46,880 --> 00:13:48,166
"Hollowface
dressed up as a man"

121
