to the boy's house."

122
00:13:50,240 --> 00:13:51,685
"He ran up
the wall quickly."

123
00:13:52,480 --> 00:13:54,562
"He slipped
through an open window."

124
00:13:55,680 --> 00:13:57,762
"He found the boy's room
and slipped inside."

125
00:13:58,960 --> 00:14:00,086
